feat(assets): add update command for assets

This commit adds a new command to update asset properties:
- Add 'update' command under assets to modify asset name and description
- Implement proper validation for required flags (name and new-name)
- Add comprehensive tests for the update functionality
- Ensure backward compatibility with existing assets
- Add clear success messages for user feedback

The update command allows users to:
1. Update only the description while keeping the same name
2. Update both name and description
3. Maintain data integrity with proper validation
